Функция обучения¶

, get_model

In [50]:
def get_model(model, X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test):
    model_fit=model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    model_preds=model_fit.predict(X_test)
    y_prob = model_fit.predict_proba(X_test)[:,1]
    
    accuracy_metric=accuracy_score(y_test, model_preds)
    log_loss_metric=log_loss(y_test, model_preds)
    false_positive_rate, true_positive_rate, thresholds = roc_curve(y_test, y_prob)
    roc_auc = auc(false_positive_rate, true_positive_rate)
    
    metrics={'':accuracy_metric, ' ':log_loss_metric, ' ':roc_auc}
    
    # 
    plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
    plt.title('  (Roc-curve)  ' + str(model))
    plt.plot(false_positive_rate,true_positive_rate, color='red',label = 'AUC = %0.2f' % roc_auc)
    plt.legend(loc = 'lower right')
    plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1],linestyle='--')

    plt.ylabel('      ')
    plt.xlabel('      ')
    plt.show
    
    return model_fit, model_preds, metrics
